name: CNN
text:
Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg has died due to complications of metastatic pancreas cancer, the court says. She was 87.

Here's a look back at her life and legacy. https://t.co/27yPHSpCGN https://t.co/tjspRs7FHt

name: CNN
text:
Ruth Bader Ginsburg was nominated to the Supreme Court in 1993 by then-Pres. Bill Clinton, and became the second woman appointed to the bench.

Her swearing in came about 12 years after Sandra Day O'Connor became the first woman to sit on the Supreme Court https://t.co/drCMPJDqAC
